{"tid":1452022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要獨立調查委員會，要終極審判香港警察","createTime":"2019-08-11T23:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T00:42:19.000Z","uid":4028,"like":90,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a73349e77a53b6c6a766c934260f62ccea53be60","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:20:30.000Z","msg":"今時今日黑警所做嘅每一件事，獨立調查係懲治唔到佢地。<br />\n香港成功抗爭以後，首先解散警隊，然後要嘅就係一個大審判，任何參與鎮壓嘅警察，依罪狀而判刑，輕則碌奪所有公民權利，重則判以極刑！<br />\n<br />\n我好希望大家要堅持落去，我知道呢幾個禮拜大家都好唔開心，但我地就係唔可以認輸！<br />\n<br />\n黑警們，你們今日犯下嘅孽，做咩都補救唔番，呢個就係同有良知嘅香港人作對嘅下場！<br />\n<br />\n大家要堅持，未到功成一日都唔可以放棄！"},{"pid":"4642903e46cbaadc3dfbc00023a33f0b58da5c7c","tid":1452022,"uid":71583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:22:28.000Z","msg":"事實已經擺在眼前，做到咁都唔駛嗰啲各打五十大板嘅調查<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199957695935775cbd6567faec14b3e84b7d3764","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4642903e46cbaadc3dfbc00023a33f0b58da5c7c","tid":1452022,"uid":71583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:22:28.000Z","msg":"事實已經擺在眼前，做到咁都唔駛嗰啲各打五十大板嘅調查<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:23:15.000Z","msg":"冇錯，我要黑警受應有嘅懲罰！"},{"pid":"fc03acf0ca0e5b83ef0ad203a967dc916a74b1ec","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:27:12.000Z","msg":"推！我地要審判黑警！"},{"pid":"542f75c535ad55525ba9d38ec3b03bf57d603246","tid":1452022,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:29:33.000Z","msg":"七警案已經證明靠現行制度去制衝班犯法狗係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e6c337b44ff1838091e1315996c52971a63311","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:31:08.000Z","msg":"獨立調查只不過係做場氣捉幾件蛋散祭旗嘅馬騮戲，唔去審判每一個黑警，對唔住每一位死士，仲有數百位被捕嘅手足！<br />\n<br />\n我要黑警餘生不得安寧！"},{"pid":"75ef38b193ee305dd4dc98e6b6d4178294d78aba","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"542f75c535ad55525ba9d38ec3b03bf57d603246","tid":1452022,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:29:33.000Z","msg":"七警案已經證明靠現行制度去制衝班犯法狗係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:35:23.000Z","msg":"七警同朱經緯更加突顯調查單一事件係無法還香港人一個公道！<br />\n我要鄉黑，支那狗，死黑警全部都不得安寧！"},{"pid":"85ab7f1dc4977d407c5bee71940e555032d35cac","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:38:00.000Z","msg":"冇一個黑警係無辜！"},{"pid":"6df3aa236fe41651793db866b9a263453d61daa7","tid":1452022,"uid":271894,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:38:48.000Z","msg":"獨立調查？<br />\n唔要了<br />\n因為3萬警察都係有罪 而且要死全家"},{"pid":"b2ace29167227078219aaa29636592eda2d57f8b","tid":1452022,"uid":83348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:39:01.000Z","msg":"why not both <br />\n<br />\n如果真係有一日有獨立調查，咪佢有佢調查，我地有我地私了做法"},{"pid":"40cd3e4ad49ea0c637af5e4d0703ea3b508705ab","tid":1452022,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:40:01.000Z","msg":"有冇國際法庭可以製裁香港警察<br />\n 宣揚香港警察戰爭罪行"},{"pid":"7477c22a147996655adb808b27f5d0022965aeed","tid":1452022,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:40:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民抗爭 背水一戰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對港鐵不合作運動全民跳閘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.勇武轉入地下打狗<br />\n<br />\n2.和理非要癱瘓機場<br />\n記住係針對貨運嚟搞!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宣佈成立國民自衛隊對抗警察</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為受傷被捕兄弟討回公道</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前線太多手足比捉 一定要升級癱瘓機場 全民打狗 選擇一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"922e1a8696a9bfa8fcd69717f8652e4099165011","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2ace29167227078219aaa29636592eda2d57f8b","tid":1452022,"uid":83348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:39:01.000Z","msg":"why not both <br />\n<br />\n如果真係有一日有獨立調查，咪佢有佢調查，我地有我地私了做法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:42:25.000Z","msg":"獨立調查，最終只會捉一少撮人出黎祭旗，但大家有眼見呢幾個禮拜，無數警想置香港人於死地<br />\n<br />\n每一個黑警都要接受審判，唔接受就判無期徒刑，要每一個黑警都毫無尊嚴咁渡過餘生！"},{"pid":"f734df0b011ee2507d7faf932808e1849e964e5c","tid":1452022,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:43:00.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"6e944411e7285d46ba7b2eaa25616deb298f495f","tid":1452022,"uid":204095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:43:56.000Z","msg":"冇理由黑社會可以咩事都冇"},{"pid":"181fa3a5168f9c8db6feb36aa1b088dc5d9c5666","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e944411e7285d46ba7b2eaa25616deb298f495f","tid":1452022,"uid":204095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:43:56.000Z","msg":"冇理由黑社會可以咩事都冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:46:08.000Z","msg":"審判已經預埋佢地，no one can escape!"},{"pid":"c363718f7031fff40bb6820beabe60f344bb843b","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:49:30.000Z","msg":"香港人，為左要見到有呢一日，一定要堅持落去！"},{"pid":"15f5bc76f8c02ce8edc8413a868bdb9a92fe65b0","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:55:18.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"3add8d705cf2b85e9792ebf3c0f2611b5a21b3c4","tid":1452022,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40cd3e4ad49ea0c637af5e4d0703ea3b508705ab","tid":1452022,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r